  "texts": [
    "Figure 3 is an additional expert from the XpertAI explanation with its native formatting.",
    "Complete explanations can be found in SI (Appendix A).",
    "This further demonstrates XpertAI's accessibility as a tool that generates credible, natural language explanations of molecular structure-property relationships.",
    "To the best of our knowledge, XpertAI is currently the only tool that combines explainable AI (XAI) with large language models (LLMs) to interpret such relationships.",
    "This illustrates how XpertAI combines features identified through XAI analysis, scientific evidence, and hypotheses to provide interpretable and targeted insights into molecular behavior."
